Ext.data.JsonP['Managing_FTP_Connections']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Managing FTP Connections</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083202\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Managing FTP Connections</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-Chapters\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Chapters</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Managing_FTP_Connections-section-src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-OpeningtheConnectionManager\">Opening the Connection Manager</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Managing_FTP_Connections-section-src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-CreatingaNewConnection\">Creating a New Connection</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Managing_FTP_Connections-section-src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-ModifyingaConnection\">Modifying a Connection</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Managing_FTP_Connections-section-src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-DeletingaConnection\">Deleting a Connection</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>Once you have created a connection, you can manage it in the Connection Manager.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-OpeningtheConnectionManager\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Opening the Connection Manager</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Select a project in the <strong class=\" \">Project Explorer</strong> View and expand it    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Right-click on the <strong class=\" \">Connections</strong> node and select <strong class=\" \">Connection Manager...</strong>    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083202/Connection_Manager.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083202/Connection_Manager.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-CreatingaNewConnection\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Creating a New Connection</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">+</strong> button at the bottom of the left pane    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select an appropriate source, either a project, or a path on the local file system    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select an appropriate destination, either a existing remote server, another project, or a place on the file system. If you do not yet have a remote server set up, click the <strong class=\" \">New</strong> button to create one.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">OK</strong>    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-ModifyingaConnection\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Modifying a Connection</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Select a connection in the list to the left    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select an appropriate source, either a project, or a path on the local file system    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select an appropriate destination, either a existing remote server, another project, or a place on the file system. If you do not yet have a remote server set up, click the <strong class=\" \">New</strong> button to create one.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">OK</strong>    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083202_ManagingFTPConnections-DeletingaConnection\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Deleting a Connection</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Select the connection you wish to remove in the left pane.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">X</strong> button at the bottom of the left pane    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Agree to the confirmation dialog.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>The connection is deleted.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">OK</strong> to exit the dialog.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083202\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Managing FTP Connections"});